&lt;li&gt;PhD in electrical engineering, physics, applied physics, or a discipline related to analog design.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Experience in designing and testing optical front-end receivers and transmitters (TIAs, drivers), CTLE, DFE, ADC, DAC, oscillators, etc. in advanced CMOS.&lt;/li&gt;
